URL = http://www.openactionnetwork.org/


=Description=

"Open Action Network is an open source, nonprofit technology initiative to enable decentralized sharing of actions and discussions across networks of websites. At the heart of the Open Action Network are the Open Action Protocols that specify standard formats for publishing, discovering, subscribing, discussing, and sharing activity around action feeds."


